client = LazopApiClient::Client.new(url, appkey, appSecret)
request = LazopApiClient::Request.new('/im/message/list','GET')
request.add_api_parameter("session_id", "100094063_2_1011822749_1_103")
request.add_api_parameter("start_time", "1623400073000")
request.add_api_parameter("page_size", "20")
request.add_api_parameter("last_message_id", "24jFlAu0BtRbP47190")
response = client.execute(request, accessToken)
puts response.success?
puts response.body

client = lazop.LazopClient(url, appkey ,appSecret)
request = lazop.LazopRequest('/im/message/list','GET')
request.add_api_param('session_id', '100094063_2_1011822749_1_103')
request.add_api_param('start_time', '1623400073000')
request.add_api_param('page_size', '20')
request.add_api_param('last_message_id', '24jFlAu0BtRbP47190')
response = client.execute(request, access_token)
print(response.type)
print(response.body)
